00:30:42,691 --> 00:30:44,730
"Rumah Sakit Sungyoga"

517
00:30:49,197 --> 00:30:50,530
Bagaimana kondisinya?

518
00:30:50,866 --> 00:30:52,600
Apa dia masih hidup?

